If neither wins, then you hold a new election, disqualifying the losers of the
previous. Or you could say "If neither was picked, then obviously nobody cares
enough that the job gets done, so we'll leave the position open."

> Uploads with unique encryption keys?  This would provide an artificial
> difference where one may not (initially) exist.  And while I agree that they
