Author(s):   Uwins PJR; Webb RI; Taylor AP 
Title: Novel nano-organisms from Australian sandstones 
Source: AMERICAN MINERALOGIST 1998, Vol 83, Iss 11-12, pp 1541-1550 
Document Type: Article 
Addresses: 
